#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Today's tip is about caring for yourself. "
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "In tough times like these, it's normal to feel overwhelmed. Remember, it is important to take a moment for yourself, no matter how small."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Taking care of yourself helps you be there for your children during tough times."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "‚ñ∂Ô∏èPress play to learn 4Ô∏è‚É£tips on how to take care of yourself: "
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "1Ô∏è‚É£**REST**"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "2Ô∏è‚É£ **CONNECT**"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "3Ô∏è‚É£**BREATHE**"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "4Ô∏è‚É£ **CARE**"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Here are 4 tips on how to take care of yourself:"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "1Ô∏è‚É£ **REST**"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Even if rest looks different right now, try to rest when you can."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Take a few minutes between responsibilities to do something that helps you relax."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Connect with loved ones as often as you can."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Find someone you can talk to about how you are feeling."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "3Ô∏è‚É£ **BREATHE**"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Take a moment each day to listen to your breath as it goes in and out."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Losing your temper? Breathe in and out slowly five times."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Make sure to take care of yourself so you can feel better and be there for your family. "
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Remember to praise yourself each time you take steps to cope."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "‚úÖ 100%"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Thank you for joining us. Remember, you're doing the best you can. Be proud."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "This tip is about making a routine for your children. "
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "When we are in crisis, things can feel unfamiliar. Having routines helps your children feel safe and stable."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "When you do the same things every day, it makes life more familiar for your children. It also makes them feel less worried and more secure."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "‚ñ∂Ô∏èPress play to learn 3Ô∏è‚É£ tips on making routines to spend time together with your children:"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "1Ô∏è‚É£ **DO IT DAILY**"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "2Ô∏è‚É£ **PLAY EVERY DAY**"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "3Ô∏è‚É£ **PRACTISE BEING CALM**"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Here are 3Ô∏è‚É£ tips on making routines to spend time together with your children:"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Even when it feels hard, try to have some activities that you and your children do every day for yourself and your children."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "If you can, daily routines like eating together and cleaning can help children feel safe, especially during uncertain times."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Try to set aside time to play or spend quality time with your children every day. "
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Playing with and talking to children for a few minutes every day helps them feel secure."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Ask children what they would like to do."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Listen to them, look at them, and give them your full attention."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Our children learn calmness and kindness from us."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Every day, try telling yourself a calming message. "
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Try ‚ÄúI can do this, I am trying my best.‚Äù"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Small amounts of time can help children feel safe and loved."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "After this lesson, you can type {PLAY} to get some activity ideas to do with children."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Here are some regular activities you might want to try to do with your children:\r\rEat one meal together"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Getting ready to sleep"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Exercise daily"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Daily play activities"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Thank you for joining us. Parenting is not always easy. Well done for doing the best you can."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "This tip is about helping your children cope with crisis. "
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "It is normal to be worried about your children, especially during tough times   "
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Children might face emotions and challenges they don‚Äôt know how to handle."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "There are things you can do to help them feel better now and make them stronger for the future."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "‚ñ∂Ô∏è Press play to learn 3Ô∏è‚É£ tips on how you can support your children during tough times: "
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "1Ô∏è‚É£ **LISTEN**"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "2Ô∏è‚É£ **PRAISE YOUR CHILDREN**"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "3Ô∏è‚É£ **PRAISE YOURSELF**"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Here are 3Ô∏è‚É£ tips on how you can support your children during tough times:"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Children may be scared, confused and angry. Simply being present and listening makes all the difference. They need your support."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Listen to your children when they share how they are feeling."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Tell them whatever they are feeling is okay, and give them comfort."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Ask children to help with day-to-day tasks, such as making food or cleaning."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Praise them for trying or doing well. This encourages helpful behaviour."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Praising children shows them that you notice and care."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Every day before you sleep, praise yourself for trying to help your children cope."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Thinking of even 1 thing you are proud of can make a difference!"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Thank you for joining us. Remember to also praise yourself for doing the best you can do."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "This tip is about helping your children when someone dies. "
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Losing a loved one is painful for everyone, including children. "
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Children may feel overwhelmed and upset when someone dies."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Talking to your children about death can be hard, but it will help them make sense of what is happening."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "‚ñ∂Ô∏èPress play 3Ô∏è‚É£ tips on how to help your children when someone dies: "
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "1Ô∏è‚É£ **BE CLEAR**"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "2Ô∏è‚É£**ACCEPT FEELINGS** "
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "3Ô∏è‚É£ **SAY GOODBYE**"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Here are 3Ô∏è‚É£ tips on how to help your children when someone dies:"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "In simple words, tell them the person has died and will not come back."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "If one of their caregivers has died, tell children who they will live with and who will look after them ‚Äì they often worry about this."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "2Ô∏è‚É£ **ACCEPT FEELINGS** "
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "There is no right way for a child to react to loss. Children may act happy but still feel sad."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Listen to your child and tell them whatever you are feeling is okay."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Do something together to say goodbye to the person ‚Äì a song, letter or prayer."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Let us understand how children of different ages react to death."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Small children under the age of 5 years may ask if the person who has died is coming back."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "They might hold onto you or other caregivers more or start doing things they used to do when they were younger, like wetting the bed."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Older children between 6 and 11 years old may ask more questions and want to understand what happened."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "They may show their grief through anger and experience physical aches or pains."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Adolescents and young teenagers from around the age of 12 years will wonder about why things happen."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Their reactions will vary and can include lack of interest, anger, extreme sadness and poor concentration."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Thank you for joining us. Parenting is full of difficult conversations. Take a moment to care for yourself."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "This tip is about protecting our children from sexual violence and responding to it. "
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "During difficult times, children are more likely to face dangers like sexual violence."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Sexual violence means doing or trying to do something sexual to someone that they don‚Äôt want to happen. "
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "This can include things like threatening, pressuring or forcing someone to have sex, or touching them in a sexual way.  "
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Sexual violence can be committed by a stranger, a friend, or even a family member."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "‚ñ∂Ô∏èPress play to learn 6Ô∏è‚É£ tips for protecting your child from sexual violence:"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "1Ô∏è‚É£ **NO IS OK!**"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "2Ô∏è‚É£ **TELL A PERSON OF TRUST**"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "3Ô∏è‚É£ **RECOGNIZE**"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "4Ô∏è‚É£ **LISTEN**"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "5Ô∏è‚É£ **RESPOND"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "6Ô∏è‚É£ **COMFORT YOUR CHILD**"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Here are 6Ô∏è‚É£ tips for protecting your child from sexual violence:"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "1Ô∏è‚É£ *NO IS OK!*"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Teach your child that no one has the right to touch them or make them uncomfortable."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Practice saying \"NO\" loudly and strongly together. "
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Remember, you can do this with words and with body. "
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Talking about this with your child helps protect them."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "2Ô∏è‚É£ **TELL AN ADULT**"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Tell them that abusers often trick children by giving gifts, pretending to be kind and supportive to gain their trust."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Once violence happens, the abusers urge their victims to keep sexual violence a ‚Äúsecret‚Äù."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Remind them that they don‚Äôt have to keep secrets from their parents or a person they trust. "
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Tell your children they don‚Äôt need to feel ashamed about the violence they survived. It is not their fault!"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Let them know it‚Äôs always okay to talk to a trusted adult, like a parent or a teacher, if someone makes them feel uncomfortable."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "3Ô∏è‚É£ **COMFORT YOUR CHILD**"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "If your child tells you about sexual violence, trust them."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Reassure them it‚Äôs not their fault and they are safe and loved."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "You can type {HELP} for resources if your child shares sexual violence with you."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "5Ô∏è‚É£ **RESPOND**: What might help in this situation?**"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "üî∂ You might need to help your child talk about their feelings or redirect their focus."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "‚û°Ô∏è You might need to talk about the actions that you will take together to help with what has happened. In case of sexual violence, you and Your child need to go to a medical examination. "
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "‚è∏. Right now, your child needs you to be there for them with love. Remind them that it is not their fault what other people did to them. "
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "‚úÖ Remember, you can always type {HELP} and get information about resources in your community where you may receive help."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "üå∑ It can be hard to see your child feeling upset or confused, but there is a lot you can do to support them."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "üíô If your child tells you about sexual violence, trust them."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "üíö Reassure them it‚Äôs not their fault and they are safe and loved."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "‚ù§Ô∏è Remind your child again that you love them and that together, you two will find solutions. Thank them for sharing with you."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Thank you for joining us. Talking about sexual violence with your children will go a long way to protect them. It is not easy but necessary. They are lucky to have you. Be proud of yourself."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Keeping children safe can feel overwhelming, especially when dealing with unexpected challenges."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "In such moments, having a clear plan will help you and your children know what to do to be safe."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Press Play ‚ñ∂Ô∏è to learn 3Ô∏è‚É£ tips on how to keep your children safe in an unsafe situation:"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "1Ô∏è‚É£ **TALK**"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "2Ô∏è‚É£ **PLAN**"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "3Ô∏è‚É£ **ASSURE**"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Here are 3Ô∏è‚É£ tips on how to keep your children safe in an unsafe situation:"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Talk to children about what is happening in a way that they can understand."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Talk to them about things that are not safe."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Identify a meeting point and make a plan in case you get separated."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Keep children with you or with someone you trust all the time."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Planning with children helps them feel safer too."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Assure your children that you will do everything to keep them safe."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Encourage them to share anything that worries them with you."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Be proud of your efforts and try to take care of yourself too."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Thank you for joining us. Remember that you are not alone and that there are things you can do to keep your children safe."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Having to travel with children during a crisis can feel scary and hard. "
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "When your children see that you're prepared, it can make them feel more stable even when things around them seem uncertain"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "There are ways to help keep your children away from harm while you are on the move."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Your child will feel reassured knowing you have a plan of action."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Press Play ‚ñ∂Ô∏è to learn 2Ô∏è‚É£ things you can do to ensure that you and your children are as safe as possible when you are travelling in a crisis situation:"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "1Ô∏è‚É£ **MOVE SAFELY**"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "2Ô∏è‚É£ **TAKE CARE OF YOURSELF**"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Here are 2Ô∏è‚É£ things you can do to ensure that you and your children are as safe as possible when you are travelling in a crisis situation:"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Travel with a group of people you know where possible."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "If you need to show your passport or ID, try to keep it in your hands."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "When it's hard, remember you're trying your best in a difficult situation."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Be sure to look after yourself too."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Thank you for joining us. You are making a difference to the safety of your children."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Human trafficking is when someone is tricked, forced, or pressured into doing something they don‚Äôt want to do for someone else‚Äôs benefit. "
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "This can include being forced to work, commit crimes,  perform sexual acts or anything else that is harmful so the human trafficker can gain money or favours. "
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "It can happen to anyone, anywhere, including in proximity to your own home."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Sometimes, children may not realise that they are being tricked by traffickers. They might be scared to report the adult who is threatening them. "
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "This lesson will help you protect your child by teaching them how to stay safe and what to watch out for."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Press Play ‚ñ∂Ô∏è to learn 5Ô∏è‚É£ things for you to do to help protect your children from traffickers."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "1Ô∏è‚É£ **TEACH YOUR CHILD**"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "2Ô∏è‚É£ **TRUST THEMSELVES**"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "3Ô∏è‚É£ **GET AWAY SAFELY**"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "4Ô∏è‚É£ **TALK TO TRUSTED ADULT**"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Ô∏è5Ô∏è‚É£ **TEACH YOURSELF**"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Here areÔ∏è 5Ô∏è‚É£ things for you to do to help protect your children from traffickers:"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "1Ô∏è‚É£ **TEACH YOUR CHILD** what human trafficking is and who traffickers can be."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Traffickers are people who lie or pretend to be friendly to trick children into going with them or doing things they don‚Äôt want to do. "
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Traffickers can be anyone - men, women, couples, or even someone your child knows and trusts. "
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "They might offer gifts, make big promises, give lots of compliments or ask them to keep a secret to gain trust."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "3Ô∏è‚É£ **GET AWAY SAFELY** "
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Before leaving with anyone, even someone your child knows, tell your child to make sure they feel safe. "
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Tell your child to make sure someone else knows where they are."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Teach them to not go anywhere with strangers even if they are nice to them. "
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "If they feel unsafe, teach them to stay calm. Walk away if they can, go to a safe place with people around, and ask a trusted adult or authority (like a teacher, police officer, or security guard) for help."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "4Ô∏è‚É£ **TALK TO TRUSTED ADULT** "
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Tell children to talk to a trusted adult if they feel confused or worried."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Let your child know they should tell you or another trusted adult if anyone, even someone they know: "
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "üî¥ gives them gifts"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "üî¥ makes big promises, or "
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "üî¥ asks them to keep secrets that make them feel uneasy."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Remind them they can always talk to you, no matter what."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "5Ô∏è‚É£ **TEACH YOURSELF**"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Learn how to spot signs that something might be wrong."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Watch for changes in your child‚Äôs behaviour or mood."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Also look out for if your child is:"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "üîµ Going to places that are unusual for them"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "üîµ Getting gifts or money they can‚Äôt explain"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "üîµ Hiding who they talk to or where they go"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "üîµ Getting nervous, upset, or secretive when using a phone or going online"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "These signs don‚Äôt always mean something is wrong but they are good reasons to check in with your children and show them you care"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Thank you for joining us today. Talking to children about traffickers can be hard for both you and  your children. Remember to be kind and patient with yourself and your children."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Being in a shelter can be lonely and stressful for children."
